[src:retrofit-java-lib/java-programming-language] Java servlet technology provides Web developers with a simple, consistent mechanism for extending the functionality of a Web server and for accessing existing business systems.
[src:retrofit-java-lib/java-programming-language] Servlets are server-side Java EE components that generate responses to requests from clients.
